{"tid":1985262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大專生涉攜汽油彈還柙 數日後警長被揭疑「編導」 控方今不反對大專生保釋","createTime":"2020-04-23T04:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T06:01:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a45d24da360e8d32e320204f49d282d9497e9ede","tid":1985262,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）一名21歲學生在上周一（4月13日）晚，在葵涌警署附近遭截查時搜出兩支懷疑汽油彈，案件上周四（17日）提堂，被告不獲准保釋，還柙至今日解往西九龍裁判法院申請保釋。控方今稱，案件「有新進展」，雖被告有招認，但須時調查及化驗證物，現不再反對被告保釋。<br />\n<br />\n就讀運動科學高級文憑的學生林偉豪（21歲），被控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。控罪指林於本年4月13日在葵芳邨正葵樓外的公眾地方攜有兩樽思疑汽油彈。被告暫毋須答辯，案件押後至6月11日再提堂。<br />\n<br />\n案件提堂兩日後，警方向傳媒確認，一名38歲警長以妨礙司法公正罪名被捕。據了解，該警長涉嫌「自編自導」上述案件，現獲警方保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n林偉豪獲准以2萬元保釋，期間不准離港、須交出旅遊證件、每周3次到警署報到及居於報稱住址。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC827/2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072748&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=65650f74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072748&h=54bd8699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072748</a>"},{"pid":"ae76e3d089970baf2fe60627a2e114f74cd2f35c","tid":1985262,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=13f58764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm4FxNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai